{"tid":370973,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"雞髀都係炸好食","createTime":"2017-08-23T10:54:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-29T13:31:31.000Z","uid":139613,"like":22,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"73ead719e518d915f41c1b20efd8f33cb4f46688","tid":370973,"uid":139613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T10:54:51.000Z","msg":"但係好油   本人基本很少食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41309e5ea43cee92b1aa0f3fc0bb8f2b45644886","tid":370973,"uid":48076,"like":30,"dislike":3,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T10:57:43.000Z","msg":"梗係燒既最好食<br />\n仲自稱自己雞髀王<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5be40bf367c5b677b088e3e40a0d56649696153","tid":370973,"uid":34489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T11:00:21.000Z","msg":"想食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3e1a3a3ce04fa9910764a40782ea2e30c746a80","tid":370973,"uid":139613,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T11:07:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>梗係燒既最好食<br />\n仲自稱自己雞髀王<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n生炸髀係我一位舊時同學推介的<br />\n見佢食時酥脆嘅外皮應聲裂開<br />\n內裏嬌柔粉嫩嘅雞肉流濺出黃金色嘅熱油<br />\n加上誘人且獨有熱氣撲鼻而來<br />\n嗰一下我就知 雞髀王非炸髀莫屬<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/23/190717_f6cbfbe52fd71d57c8ebfb7b62454bc1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F23%2F190717_f6cbfbe52fd71d57c8ebfb7b62454bc1.jpg&h=128f7a62&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ca16fdefc70b417973a2a606004a86f7fb7a4f20","tid":370973,"uid":102096,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T11:23:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ba42d54321433442a5c29505b275873182d3769d","tid":370973,"uid":92783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T11:25:18.000Z","msg":"邊到有好食炸脾推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3913a622a783bde5fc93ef7e57588e14e0f510e9","tid":370973,"uid":77092,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T11:28:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ee47b744216bc9d58e230a69e1405177b3dc110d","tid":370973,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T11:28:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>邊到有好食炸脾推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n土瓜灣，天光道 喜 喜 喜 喜，都叫入得口，如遇即炸就更佳"},{"pid":"86a7aa6f7696e331b3651abea0ab85ef076c3716","tid":370973,"uid":57835,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T11:29:26.000Z","msg":"鍾意食滷水髀多啲喎"},{"pid":"43db6876cfeccc52aa0e4da3ac769984e1c6a42e","tid":370973,"uid":9887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T11:46:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>炸脾一味落d粉落去根本到到食都一樣<br />\n但豉油脾就唔同<br />\n功夫講究好多</blockquote><br />\n炸髀落粉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"492c296bdcd28eb0c2f4caeeb1d215524851e817","tid":370973,"uid":139613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T11:49:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>炸脾一味落d粉落去根本到到食都一樣<br />\n但豉油脾就唔同<br />\n功夫講究好多</blockquote><br />\n炸髀落粉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n炸髀都有質感可言的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38ee851c0f722fcb02ffc87d082f2cf2e8fbad6b","tid":370973,"uid":13718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T11:49:22.000Z","msg":"你食過北角嗰間未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e1ffe7048848d1ca909400ca1e8fea04894544e","tid":370973,"uid":52252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T14:59:34.000Z","msg":"識食緊係食白切雞脾"},{"pid":"c96256b5a8c957224174a581f4c793ace728b376","tid":370973,"uid":119330,"like":5,"dislike":1,"scor